Change History

Revision Date Notes
11.0.2 2021-03-01 Added result ErrorUnsupportedWANType to action SetIPv6Settings2.
11.0.1 2020-07-07 Added Router12 service for configuration of WAN2 settings.

Added the following:
  • action GetWAN2Status
  • action GetWAN2Settings
  • action SetWAN2Settings
  • action GetDualWANEnable
  • action SetDualWANEnable
11.0.0 2019-07-17 Added Router11 service to indicate the following actions now require authentication:
  • GetEthernetPortConnections
  • GetLANSettings
  • GetDHCPClientLeases
  • GetIPv6Settings
  • GetIPv6Settings2
  • GetMACAddressCloneSettings
  • GetRoutingSettings
  • GetStaticRoutingTable
  • GetExpressForwardingSettings
10.0.0 2019-01-25 Added service Router10 with action GetWANSettings5, which returns a vlantagging:SinglePortVLANTaggingSettings2 structure.
9.0.1 2018-06-13 InitiateWirelessConnection is no longer safe to be called in a transaction.
9.0.0 2017-03-26 Added Router9 service to indicate bridge mode support in newer Nodes FW.
NOTE: This a service revision only -- no other changes.
8.0.1 2017-06-20 Move optional lanPrefixAddress to output of GetWANStatus3, and remove struct IPv6NetworkInfo2
8.0.0 2017-01-20 Added Router8 service for configuring WAN settings with optional VLAN tagging.

Introduced:
  • action GetWANSettings4
  • action SetWANSettings4
  • error ErrorWANTaggingNotSupported
Router7 has been deprecated.
7.0.0 2016-03-16 Added Router7 service.

Consolidated Router4 and Router6. Introduced:
  • action GetWANSettings3
Router3, Router4, and Router6 have been deprecated.
6.0.0 2015-11-15 Added Router6 service that supports express forwarding.

Added the following:
  • enum GetExpressForwardingSettings
  • struct SetExpressForwardingSettings
5.0.0 2015-02-23 Added Router5 service that supports configuring PPPoE and Pass-through on IPv6.

Added the following:
  • enum WANIPv6Type2
  • struct SupportedWANCombination
  • struct WANIPv6ConnectionInfo2
  • struct IPv6NetworkInfo2
  • struct IPv6AutomaticSettings
  • action GetIPv6Settings2
  • action SetIPv6Settings2
  • action GetWANStatus3
  • error ErrorMissingIPv6AutomaticSettings
  • error ErrorSuperfluousIPv6AutomaticSettings

GetLANSettings

http://linksys.com/jnap/router/GetLANSettings
This action gets router settings related to LAN management.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
ipAddress IPAddress no The IP address of the router on the LAN. If isDHCPEnabled is true, this is also the DHCP server's IP address.
networkPrefixLength int no The network prefix length of the LAN.
minNetworkPrefixLength int no The minimum supported network prefix length of the LAN.
maxNetworkPrefixLength int no The maximum supported network prefix length of the LAN.
hostName string no The desired host name of the router on the LAN.
minAllowedDHCPLeaseMinutes int no The minimum allowed length, in minutes, of a DHCP lease.
maxAllowedDHCPLeaseMinutes int yes The maximum allowed length, in minutes, of a DHCP lease. If this value is not present, there is no upper limit on the DHCP lease time.
maxDHCPReservationDescriptionLength int no The maximum length, in bytes, of the description member of a DHCP reservation.
isDHCPEnabled bool no Whether the router is currently acting as a DHCP server for other devices on the LAN.
dhcpSettings DHCPSettings no Configurable settings of the router's DHCP server.

Result
